invariant abc_extra207.update_abstractmethods.qualname_eq:
  description: "abc.update_abstractmethods.__qualname__.__eq__('update_abstractmethods') == True — update_abstractmethods is a top-level function added in Python 3.10 to recalculate abstract methods; its qualname equals its simple name; new to abc_extra207; verified Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  category: qualnames
